    "pin_assignment_note": "On TC387 (TC38x family) LFBGA-516, GTM TOM1 channels 1..6 are not routed to P00.2–P00.7. Per Infineon mapping table IfxGtm_PinMap_TC38x_LFBGA516, the functions available on these pins are TOUT11..TOUT16, which correspond to TOM1 channels 5..10. The design therefore uses TOM1 CH5..10 to preserve the requested P00.2–P00.7 locations and maintain complementary adjacency."
